On the Monday edition of the Alex Jones Show, Alex talks about the fact Ron Paul is the Republican presidential front-runner despite an all-out effort by the political establishment and the corporate media to marginalize and ignore him. Alex also talks about Rick Perry's entrance into the race over the weekend and Perry's effort to portray himself as a conservative Christian Tea Party leader when in fact he is a one-world globalist and former Al Gore campaign manager.
